When I became a mama, my skincare priorities changed overnight. I wanted fewer steps, safer ingredients, and no compromises. 💛

With @orimiiskincare  I found a routine that’s made with plant-based ingredients, no artificial fragrances, no harsh chemicals… just pure, gentle love. 🌿👶

My glow-to routine:
🧼 Gentle clay cleanser
💧 No-retinol serum
💦  Babysoft ceramide Moisturizer
🧴 Pure Watery Mineral sunscreen
💋 First Kiss Moisturising Lip balm

This isn’t just skincare — it’s self-care, reimagined for motherhood.
With @orimiiskincare, I know I’m doing right by my skin and my baby. 💫
